data.description: Updated ranch with over $15,000 in recent improvements! Newly surfaced drywall throughout. Large livingroom with ceiling fan and new laminate flooring opens to spacious kitchen with dining area. Rec room style basement with new furnace, central air and new 100 amp breaker box in 2012. Fresh paint throughout, stove refrigerator, washer & dryer included. Currently has a dishwasher but seller not sure of condition. Nice lot with peach tree and picnic table. Roof new in 2007, detached over-sized single garage with opener.
